      "description": "Five-fold cross-validation performed on the full 1,240-sample dataset. RMSE = 0.038 across folds, with fold-to-fold standard deviation of 0.004. Folds were constructed by random shuffling; temporal or geometric stratification was not applied. Results are reported as evidence of model stability within the training distribution.",
      "metricName": "Root Mean Squared Error — Relative Hemolysis Index",
