      "rationale": "The CFD solver used to generate training data has been verified against FDA benchmark nozzle and lid-driven cavity cases. The gradient-boosted regressor implementation (scikit-learn 1.3) is a widely verified open-source library. Code-level unit tests confirm feature scaling and tree-construction logic. Gradation 1 requirement is satisfied."
