      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation was applied to three mesh densities (2.1 M, 5.4 M, 11.2 M cells). The grid-convergence index (GCI) for area-averaged wall shear stress is below 1.8% at all five operating points. Discretization error is adequately characterized for the CFD data used to train the surrogate."
