      "rationale": "In vitro hemolysis experiments used bovine blood at hematocrit 35±1.5%, 37°C, across the five target flow-speed combinations. Pump inlet pressure was controlled to ±3 mmHg. Test conditions are representative of the COU operating envelope. Gradation 2 is achieved."
