      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Surrogate-predicted RH values agree with experimental RH within ±10% across all nominal validation operating points.",
      "rationale": "At all five nominal operating points, the surrogate RH predictions fall within 6.2% of experimental measurements (maximum deviation 8.7% at 6 L/min, 4000 RPM). Agreement is within the ±10% acceptance band. Gradation 2 is satisfied for the nominal-condition validation set."
