      "rationale": "The surrogate directly predicts the normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) and derived RH, which are the quantities specified in the FDA guidance for CPB device evaluation. Secondary QoIs (area-averaged shear stress, exposure time) are used as model inputs and are traceable to the hemolysis power-law model. QoI relevance is confirmed at Gradation 2."
    },
